<num value="56">己未</num>
<pc>，</pc>遣使隸囚<pc>。</pc>是月<pc>，</pc>放進士劉瓘等<measure quantity="13" unit="people">
<num value="13">百一十三</num>人</measure>
<pc>。</pc>秋<measure quantity="7" unit="months">
