<measure quantity="11" unit="months">
<num value="11">十一</num>月</measure>
<num value="14">丁丑</num>
<pc>，</pc>召沙門守道開壇於內殿<pc>。</pc>
<num value="20">癸未</num>
<pc>，</pc>復南京流民差役<measure quantity="3" unit="years">
<num value="3">三</num>年</measure>
<pc>，</pc>被火之家免租稅<measure quantity="1" unit="year">
<num value="1">一</num>年</measure>
<pc>。</pc>
<measure quantity="12" unit="months">
<num value="12">十二</num>月</measure>
<num value="43">丙午</num>
<pc>，</pc>彗星犯尾<pc>。</pc>
<num value="52">乙卯</num>
<pc>，</pc>幸西京<pc>。</pc>
<num value="55">戊午</num>
<pc>，</pc>行再生禮<pc>，</pc>赦雜犯死罪以下<pc>。</pc>
</p>
</div>
<div>
<p>
