<measure quantity="12" unit="months">
<num value="12">十二</num>月</measure>
<num value="4">丁卯</num>
<pc>，</pc>武定軍<term>節度使</term>耶律仁傑以罪削爵為民<pc>。</pc>
<num value="8">辛未</num>
