<measure quantity="6" unit="months">
<num value="6">六</num>月</measure>
<num value="48">辛亥</num>朔<pc>，</pc>駐蹕納葛濼<pc>。</pc>
<num value="53">丙辰</num>
<pc>，</pc>夏國遣使來貢<pc>。</pc>
<num value="54">丁巳</num>
<pc>，</pc>以耶律頗德為北院<term>樞密使</term>
